oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Top of the Charts
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (black, red, and yellow on white) announcing Top of the Charts featuring Tony Adams, Andy Atkinson, Gene Austin, Lynn Avery, Dan Beblo, Paige Beige, Debby Buggs, Patty Bullington, Marcia Burris, Dave Carter, Jeff Carter, Derek Casper, Jack Clarke, Chuck Crawford, George Cross, Steve Curtis, Robin Divita, Mark Duke, Pam Elsasser, Kay Evans, Morry Feldman, Donnie Ferguson, Pam Giles, Stefanie Greenwood, Bob Hammond, Jim Harris, Judi Heady, Michelle Hemphill, Maury Hill, Jeff Kodytek, Corinne Kupris, Randy Lykes, Jerry Machovina, JoAnn Magill, Dale Manning, Jim Mason, Derek Mattsson, Patrick McGrath, Dwight McCune, Sheryl Miller, Sanjiv More', Sharon, Nicholson, Maureen O'Hanlon, Lucinda Peters, Michael Phillips, Pete Pickering, Rita Powell, Mike Prescott, Jessica Pritt, Brett Rice, Darlene Salonia, Amy Schelton, Mark Schmiedeknecht, Jean Secrest, Melody Silvers, Dana Skulan, Dave Solomon, Rick Steele, Billy Stewart, Todd Stewart, Barbara Terry, Kathy Usery, Roger Weaver, Gordon Weingarth, Bill West, and Audrey Wiseman in Nashville, Tennessee on April 14-18. Poster features woodcuts of stars.
